Title: S and S Northern Merlin gas pressure proving and detection system
Description: For use in plant rooms and boiler houses, this S and S Northern Merlin gas pressure proving and gas detection system panel carries out a gas proving test on pipework, letting you know if there is a gas appliance open or a gas leak. A lockable key switch operation gives the user full control over their incoming gas supply.

Title: Siemens outside air temperature detector
Description: Ideal for heating, ventilating and air conditioning plants where comfort is required, this Siemens outside temperature sensor reads the air temperature via a sensing element which changes resistance as a function of the temperature, delivering to a suitable controller.

Title: Siemens immersion temperature sensor with packet
Description: Suitable for use in ventilation and air conditioning plants, this Siemens immersion temperature sensor can control or limit flow temperatures, limit return temperatures and control DHW temperatures. Reading the medium temperature via a resistance changing sensing element, the sensor then passes the reading to a controller.

Title: Siemens duct temperature detection 0.4m sensor
Description: Suitable for use in ventilation and air conditioning plants, this Siemens 0.4M duct temperature sensor can operate as a supply or extract air temperature sensor, a limit sensor, reference sensor or as a measuring sensor. Reading the air temperature via a resistance changing sensing element, the sensor then passes the reading to a controller.

Title: S and S Northern Merlin 2 zone gas detection system (up to 8 sensors)
Description: Operating on two zone gas detection, this S and S Northern Merlin gas detection system can connect two remote detectors for multi-area or multi-gas detection in factories, car parks, boiler houses or shopping centres, commonly sensing carbon monoxide, natural gas or LPG. The Merlin gas detection range is capable of incorporating any number of fusible links wired in series to the same terminal for extra peace of mind.

Title: S and S Northern Merlin carbon monoxide gas sensor (for S-Range and GDP systems)
Description: Operating with a control panel, this S and S Northern Merlin carbon monoxide detector should be situated approximately 1M from ground level to properly sense dense carbon monoxide. Suitable for use with S-Range and GDP Systems, when this detector senses carbon monoxide at a level exceeding 50ppm for over 4 minutes it will trigger and alarm which is resettable by rectifying the leak, allowing the sensor head to clear and restarting the panel.

Title: Coster methane gas sensor commercial
Description: This Coster gas sensor monitors the concentration of combustible gas in the air and activates a voltage output to an electronic detector. It is compatible with RFG 361, RFG 651, RFG 652 and RFG 653.

Title: S and S Northern Merlin gas sensor (for S-Range and GDP systems)
Description: Designed to work with a control panel, this S and S Northern Merlin natural gas detector is compatible with S-Range and GDP systems. This natural gas detector should be located around 300mm from the ceiling and at detection will go into alarm at 10% of the low explosion level, triggering isolation of the power supply to the solenoid and therefore isolation of the gas supply.

Title: Siemens clamp on water temperature detector
